To test the software without 1-wire devices run the following command:

owserver --fake=DS18B20,DS2406 --foreground --nozero -p 12345

In your mashctld.conf.simul set owparms to localhost:12345

You should now be able to use the software with the
random temperature values generated by owserver.

To use the new (random) sensor ID's update the configuration file
for the simulation as follows:
./mashctld -l -w -c mashctld.conf.simul

Afterwords run:
./mashctld -d -c mashctld.conf.simul


